targets.rawSql:
SELECT timestamp, volume, keyword 
FROM `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.GoogleTrends.realtime_trends_timelines_r` 
WHERE category = "$Category"
AND keyword = "$Keyword"
ORDER BY timestamp ASC

SELECT * 
FROM `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.GoogleTrends.realtime_trends_r` 
WHERE 
--  category ='Business'
  category = 'Headlines'
--  category = 'Science_Tech'
--  category = 'Sport'
--  category = 'Entertainment'
--  category = 'Health'
AND timestamp = 
  (SELECT MAX(timestamp) 
  FROM `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.GoogleTrends.realtime_trends_r`)
ORDER BY rank

SELECT
  keyword as trend, rank
FROM
  `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.GoogleTrends.realtime_trends_r`
--timestamp = DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE(), INTERVAL 0 DAY) 
WHERE  EXTRACT(DATE FROM DATETIME(timestamp, "Europe/Berlin")) = EXTRACT(DATE FROM DATETIME_SUB(CURRENT_DATE("Europe/Berlin"), INTERVAL 1 DAY))  
AND category = "Headlines"
--DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE()\, INTERVAL  1 DAY),
LIMIT
  50

FROM `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.GoogleTrends.realtime_trends_r`

--  category = 'Science_Tech'
--  category = 'Sport'
--  category = 'Entertainment'

AND timestamp =
